Over the last few years, I have spent a lot of time writing (see some [vanity
metrics](/stats/)), mostly about tech, but also about some other topics from
time to time.

- 🕵️‍♀️ If you are looking for something specific, use [the search](/blog/search/).
- 🦸‍♀️ Otherwise, we have lovely [guest posts](/blog/guest/).
- 🧑‍🍳 I’ve also published some of my own [recipes](/blog/recipes/).
- 👩‍💻 For *code* recipes, head to the [snippets](/snippets/) section.

